$OpenBSD$

+-----------------------------------------------------------------------
| Running ${FULLPKGNAME} on OpenBSD
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------

Quick start
===========

To load irssi-otr type in the IRSSI main window
    /load libotr

To initiate OTR session open a chat window and type
    /otr init

For further detail please refer to
${PREFIX}/share/irssi/help/otr
